## REVERSE STRING

class ReverseString {
public static void main(String[] args) {
String s = "hello";
String rev = "";

```
    for (int i = s.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
        rev += s.charAt(i);
    }

    System.out.println(rev);
}
```

}

