## PALINDROME CHECK

class Palindrome {
public static void main(String[] args) {
String s = "madam";

```
    int left = 0, right = s.length() - 1;
    boolean isPal = true;

    while (left < right) {
        if (s.charAt(left) != s.charAt(right)) {
            isPal = false;
            break;
        }
        left++;
        right--;
    }

    System.out.println(isPal);
}
```

}

